<br>
I have a Breaking News Flash, that I wanted to share with every one on the message boards.<br>
<br>
We are starting a new business down below in the Metro Detroit Area.   Our new business venture will be owned and operated by my family, who are all Sault Tribal Members.   We have signed on to become a new dealership, for a major U.S. based ATV manufacturing company, that manufactures Amphibious All Terrain Vehicles.   We will be marketing, selling, and servicing the Max Brand Amphibious All Terrain Vehicle Product line, for the Recreative Industries Company based in Buffalo, New York.    <br>
<br>
The Max Brand name ATV's are a very fine example of a well designed, and well built American made products.   Needless to say, we are very excited about this new opportunity and business venture.   Our new Max ATV dealership will be named [b]"Motown ATV's"[/b].   Our new dealership will be located in the downriver area of Taylor, Michigan.    We plan to run the new business out of our home, which will allow us to keep our over head costs under control, and will also give us the ability to do more advertising.<br>
<br>
Our exclusive dealership area will encompass a huge portion of the Southeastern Michigan Area.   We will also be allowed to market and sell units any where out of our area, that we wish to do business.   We are currently in the process of constructing a very nice web site for the new dealership, and it should be available on line within the next couple of weeks.   Our new dealership web site address will be located at www.motownatvs.com.<br>
<br>
I want to say that we are probably the first and only, Native American own and operated, Amphibious All Terrain Dealership in the entire country.<br>
<br>
I invite you to please visit our web site, when we are up and running.   If there is any one interested in these types of ATV products, please do not hesitate to contact us at any time.   We are backed up and supported very well, by an excellent U.S.A. based company, that knows how to make quality products, and provides outstanding aftermarket service to their customers.<br>
<br>
We will be starting to take new ATV orders very soon, and we will also be able to drop ship units just about any where on the planet, for very reasonable prices!<br>
<br>
We Thank You very much for reading this announcement and listening to what we will have to offer.   We look forward to hearing from and meeting new people and providing excellent services to our customers.<br>
<br>
Thank You<br>
